
Description

Add advanced AI capabilities to Ghost-Mux to transform it into an intelligent software engineering platform that goes beyond terminal multiplexing and AI assistance.

Proposed Features

- Multi-Agent AI Collaboration (Coding Agent, Debugging Agent, Testing Agent, Documentation Agent)
- Explainable AI for code suggestions and recommendations
- Predictive Bug Detection using Machine Learning
- Knowledge Graph for project context and dependency management
- Digital Twin for simulating code changes before deployment
- AI-Powered Code Review and Optimization
- Automatic Documentation Generation
- Natural Language Command Interface
- IDE Integration (VS Code and other editors)
- Real-Time Team Collaboration Dashboard

Expected Benefits

- Faster and more efficient software development
- Improved code quality and maintainability
- Better understanding of AI-generated recommendations
- Enhanced collaboration between developers and AI agents
- Support for research-oriented and enterprise-scale development workflows

Suggested Project Titles

1. Explainable Multi-Agent AI-Powered Software Engineering Platform Using Ghost-Mux
2. Intelligent Multi-Agent Development Environment with Knowledge Graph Analytics
3. AI-Driven Collaborative Software Engineering Platform Using Digital Twin Technology
4. Explainable AI-Based Integrated Development Environment with Multi-Agent Collaboration
